  "detailed_description": "Experience interdimensional love in this unique visual novel! This visual novel comes with three different play styles!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Make choices!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Write poems!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">• Turn-based RPG styled battles!</ul><br>Two girls from another dimension have appeared in your room! And it's raining sakura petals...? What is going on?<br><br>Find out more about the girls as you try to find a way back to their own dimensions. Or... would you like them to stay with you instead? <br><br>Win your girl's heart by talking, writing or battling into their heart!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373270/extras/165f31b464e2baeffd1e3e76166b7163.avif?t=1686526961\" width=603 height=280 /></span>",
